ApproxsimClient.TaclanV2
Class ParsedDeclaration

java.lang.Object
  ApproxsimClient.TaclanV2.ParsedObject
      ApproxsimClient.TaclanV2.ParsedDeclaration
Direct Known Subclasses:
ParsedList, ParsedPrimitive
public class ParsedDeclaration
extends ParsedObject

An object representing a declaration in the Taclan V2 language. As a parsed construct it contains artefacts of the language, e. g. references to the source files
